#

Arugula and Cherry Tomato Salad

10 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladQuickHealthy

Description

A fresh and vibrant salad that combines peppery arugula with sweet cherry tomatoes, dressed with a simple vinaigrette.

Ingredients

  • arugula: 4 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • parmesan cheese (optional): 1/4 cup, shaved
